datapacks.name: Brevman Character Pack V3
datapacks.author: Brevman
datapacks.description:
A assortment of characters that I've made!
Tries to have a variety of all types, inmates, guards, engineers, nurses, etc. From the kind and gentle, to the utterly brutal. From the submissive to those that will crush you under their boot.
Every single character is highly customised, with unique attacks, loot tables, and detailed descriptions with backstory.
16 fem, 12 male, 6 andro II 20 inmates, 7 guards, 4 engineers, 3 nurses
Most of them are higher level, 8-50 so far. Most are 20+ (Plus a single lvl 80 "boss") The pack is meant to make the early levels rough, and lvl20+ no longer trivial.
Can you handle the challenge? ;P
